FAQs
How can I apply to Tbilisi State Medical University?

You can apply to TSMU by submitting an online application through the university’s official website. Ensure you meet the eligibility criteria and provide all required documents.

What are the tuition fees for international students?

Tuition fees vary depending on the program and level of study. Detailed information can be found on the university’s website or by contacting the admissions office.

Is there on-campus accommodation available?

Yes, TSMU offers on-campus dormitories and other accommodation options to meet the diverse needs of students.

What kind of support is provided to international students?

TSMU offers various support services including orientation programs, academic advising, and counseling services to help international students adjust and succeed.

How can I contact the admissions office?

You can contact the admissions office via the contact information provided on the TSMU official website or by emailing their admissions department directly.
